properties.Name: BreachBehaviorType
properties.Description:
A customer action that is violation of the terms and conditions of the associated account.

Ex:
- Failure to pay monthly billing
- Failure to pay maintenance billing
- Bad check
- Insufficient Funds
- Account Application Contains Incorrect Information
- Credit Application Contains Incorrect Information
- Incorrect Billing Information Provided
- Used Incorrect Account For Reservation
- Violation of terms and conditions
